table.name: YG_DEVICE_CTRL
table.Comment: 存储用户对设备操作指令集

table.name: YG_SMS_RECORD
table.Comment: 短信发送记录,有次数限定时使用

table.name: time_zone_leap_second
table.Comment: Leap seconds information for time zones

column.name: Valid_Ctrl
column.Comment: 账户控制状态：0、失效、1、生效

column.name: Role_Status
column.Comment: 角色状态：0：新建、1：启用、2：停用

column.name: Alipy_Status
column.Comment: 付款状态：0未付款，1已付款

column.name: Device_SALE_Name
column.Comment: 销售名称（网站地图标记用命）

column.name: Install_Status
column.Comment: 安装码状态：0未绑定，1绑定，2失效

column.name: Menu_Description
column.Comment: 菜单描述（例如：车辆监控页面车辆右键菜单；车辆监控页面代理商右键菜单；）

column.name: Operation_Code
column.Comment: 操作编码 注：操作取值为 页面ID+元素类型+操作名 例如：LBSMENUDELETE

column.name: Permission_Type
column.Comment: 权限类型(0：菜单,1：页面,2：操作)

column.name: Permission_Description
column.Comment: 权限描述 例如：车辆监控页面右键菜单删除按钮隐藏

column.name: Role_Type
column.Comment: 可以设置多级用户，首版三级用户没有创建下级用户功能：（0：系统管理员）

column.name: User_Name
column.Comment: 用户名称：比如：广东省XX电动车代理商_高XX

column.name: Group_Name
column.Comment: 组名称：每个用户下面会有一个默认组，未卖出去的设备会放入默认组里面；若统计库存，直接统计该用户默认组下的设备数量。

column.name: Dev_Type
column.Comment: 登录设备类型：1 for web, 2 for pc, 3 for android, 4 for ios, 5 for wp

column.name: Dev_AppId
column.Comment: 设备推送APPID，APPID 对应唯一一台设备

column.name: Dev_Type
column.Comment: 登录设备类型：1 for web, 2 for pc, 3 for android, 4 for ios, 5 for wp

column.name: Dev_AppId
column.Comment: 设备推送APPID，APPID 对应唯一一台设备

column.name: Act_Status
column.Comment: 状态：0：新建、1：发布、2：审核未通过、3：过期

column.name: Space_Time
column.Comment: 最后查询结束时间：单位（秒）

column.name: Gps_Number
column.Comment: 时间段内的GPS点数量：单位（个）

column.name: Create_Time
column.Comment: 当日时间：当天添加本记录的时间

column.name: Alarm_Type
column.Comment: 告警类型：1、震动告警、2、强开锁告警、3、车轮滚动告警、4、围栏告警、5、位移告警、6、断电/断线告警

column.name: Ctrl_Status
column.Comment: 指令状态：0：等待、1：成功、2：失败

column.name: RT_Track_Interval
column.Comment: 实时GPS上传&获取时间，单位：秒

column.name: FT_Track_Interval
column.Comment: 定时上传GPS时间，单位：分钟

column.name: Up_Retry_Times
column.Comment: 上传数据失败重试次数

column.name: Wait_Sleep_Time
column.Comment: 等待休眠时间，单位：分钟

column.name: Gps_Reboot_Time
column.Comment: GPS模块定时重启时间，单位分钟

column.name: Net_Retry_Interval
column.Comment: 网络连接失败，重试时间间隔，单位：分钟

column.name: Socket_HBeat_Interval
column.Comment: 长连接心跳周期，单位：秒

column.name: Shake_St_Time1
column.Comment: 震动开始时间，单位：毫秒

column.name: Shake_End_Time1
column.Comment: 震动终止时间，单位：毫秒

column.name: Device_Defence_Status
column.Comment: 设防状态 1设防；0解防 缺省为设防 解防预制：设备休眠情况，状态为解防预制，App端显示触碰响铃后解防。

column.name: Device_Mobility_Status
column.Comment: 设备移动状态： 0：静止 1：行进 2：休眠 缺省为休眠

column.name: Device_Ptl_Elec_Status
column.Comment: 设备油电状态：1、通油通电、0、断油熄火

column.name: Device_Elec_Defence_Value_Upd_Time
column.Comment: 电子围栏范围更新时间

column.name: Device_Broke_Upd_Time
column.Comment: 设备是否已更新参数：0、未更新\n1、已更新

column.name: Device_PL_Rmd
column.Comment: 低电提醒状态： 提醒：1 不提醒：0 缺省为1

column.name: Device_PL_Rmd_Upd_Time
column.Comment: 低电提醒状态更新时间

column.name: Device_OvrSpd_Rmd
column.Comment: 超速提醒状态： 提醒：1 不提醒：0 缺省为1

column.name: Device_OvrSpd_Rmd_Upd_Time
column.Comment: 超速状态提醒更新时间

column.name: Device_Roll_Rmd
column.Comment: 车轮滚动报警设置：0：关闭,1：开启

column.name: Device_Roll_Rmd_Upd_Time
column.Comment: 车轮滚动报警设置更新时间

column.name: Device_Ctrl_Model
column.Comment: 控车模式：0、省电模式；1、超爽模式

column.name: Device_Rmd_Voice
column.Comment: 设备告警喇叭声音开关：0、关闭；1、开启。默认1开启

column.name: Gps_Number
column.Comment: 时间段内的GPS点数量：单位（个）

column.name: Space_Time
column.Comment: GPS查询的结束时间：单位（毫秒）

column.name: Gps_Number
column.Comment: 时间段内的GPS点数量：单位（个）

column.name: Thread_Start_Time
column.Comment: 线程开始时间：单位（毫秒）

column.name: Thread_End_Time
column.Comment: 线程结束时间：单位（毫秒）

column.name: Gps_Number
column.Comment: 时间段内的GPS点数量：单位（个）

column.name: Version_Platform
column.Comment: 客户端平台类型：3：Android、4：IOS，默认为3

column.name: Client_Device
column.Comment: 客户端版本对应机型，null为适合所有设备

column.name: Force_Updade
column.Comment: 是否强制升级：0：为不强制升级，1：强制升级

column.name: Gps_Number
column.Comment: 时间段内的GPS点数量：单位（个）

column.name: source_uuid
column.Comment: uuid of the source where the transaction was originally executed.

column.name: Number_of_lines
column.Comment: Number of lines in the file.

column.name: Master_log_name
column.Comment: The name of the master binary log currently being read from the master.

column.name: Master_log_pos
column.Comment: The master log position of the last read event.

column.name: Host
column.Comment: The host name of the master.

column.name: User_name
column.Comment: The user name used to connect to the master.

column.name: User_password
column.Comment: The password used to connect to the master.

column.name: Port
column.Comment: The network port used to connect to the master.

column.name: Connect_retry
column.Comment: The period (in seconds) that the slave will wait before trying to reconnect to the master.

column.name: Enabled_ssl
column.Comment: Indicates whether the server supports SSL connections.

column.name: Ssl_ca
column.Comment: The file used for the Certificate Authority (CA) certificate.

column.name: Ssl_capath
column.Comment: The path to the Certificate Authority (CA) certificates.

column.name: Ssl_cert
column.Comment: The name of the SSL certificate file.

column.name: Ssl_cipher
column.Comment: The name of the cipher in use for the SSL connection.

column.name: Ssl_key
column.Comment: The name of the SSL key file.

column.name: Ssl_verify_server_cert
column.Comment: Whether to verify the server certificate.

column.name: Bind
column.Comment: Displays which interface is employed when connecting to the MySQL server

column.name: Ignored_server_ids
column.Comment: The number of server IDs to be ignored, followed by the actual server IDs

column.name: Retry_count
column.Comment: Number of reconnect attempts, to the master, before giving up.

column.name: Ssl_crl
column.Comment: The file used for the Certificate Revocation List (CRL)

column.name: Ssl_crlpath
column.Comment: The path used for Certificate Revocation List (CRL) files

column.name: Enabled_auto_position
column.Comment: Indicates whether GTIDs will be used to retrieve events from the master.

column.name: Channel_name
column.Comment: The channel on which the slave is connected to a source. Used in Multisource Replication

column.name: Number_of_lines
column.Comment: Number of lines in the file or rows in the table. Used to version table definitions.

column.name: Relay_log_name
column.Comment: The name of the current relay log file.

column.name: Relay_log_pos
column.Comment: The relay log position of the last executed event.

column.name: Master_log_name
column.Comment: The name of the master binary log file from which the events in the relay log file were read.

column.name: Master_log_pos
column.Comment: The master log position of the last executed event.

column.name: Sql_delay
column.Comment: The number of seconds that the slave must lag behind the master.

column.name: Id
column.Comment: Internal Id that uniquely identifies this record.

column.name: Channel_name
column.Comment: The channel on which the slave is connected to a source. Used in Multisource Replication

column.Comment: The channel on which the slave is connected to a source. Used in Multisource Replication

column.Comment: 8:发送成功;9:发送失败;0执行成功;1执行失败
